<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #007BFF;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .otp-box {
      margin: 30px auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .otp {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 12px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: 2px dashed #007BFF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      user-select: all;
      cursor: text;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007BFF;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Your OTP Code</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification. This code is valid for the next 10 minutes.</p>
      
      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
      </div>

      <p>If you did not request this code, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ahmad Raza Khokhar. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
